headline: GoDaddy Teams Up with Prime Video to Celebrate the Fallout Series Premiere
summary: GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) is bringing an exciting online experience to fans of the Fallout series on Prime Video just in time for Season Two premiering on December 17. Through GoDaddy Airo®, fans can now explore a digital version of Ma June's Sundries, the infamous trading post and cornerstone of survival in The Wasteland.
